==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Getterup
<hw>Get"ter*up`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who contrives, makes, or
arranges for, anything, as a book, a machine, etc.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A diligent <qex>getter-up</qex> of miscellaneous works.</q>
<rj><qau>W. Irving.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Getting</ent>⟦br⟧
